title: Looking for two D5+ Junglers ! 4Leaf Team A & B
body:
Looking for a committed and dedicated player who is serious about ranked 5s and tourneys, We are a team who has already reached 2nd on the open ladder tournament.

We're looking for a Diamond 3+ jungler for Team A
and a D5 + Jungler for Team B.

You will get coaching from a experienced coach who is very close with the ex coach from Cloud 9.
We are very organised, We will do all the dirty work. You just play & win :)

Add myself (4L Rampage) Or Brad (4L Dunbt)
-Andie
